  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Form the ground beef into 4 patties, about 3/4-inch thick.",
    "Season the patties with salt and pepper.",
    "Grill the patties for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked to your desired level of doneness.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the brioche bread slices.",
    "Spread a layer of mayonnaise on each toasted bread slice.",
    "Add a cooked beef patty to each bread slice.",
    "Top each patty with a slice of melted mozzarella cheese.",
    "Add sliced tomatoes and a sprinkle of fresh basil and cilantro on top of the cheese.",
    "Drizzle the sandwiches with sesame oil and soy sauce.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
